# Install:
# --------
# 1) Edit the head var on the file (really simple).
# 2) Add exec access -> $ chmod +x slideshow-gnome-3.sh
# 3) Just run 'gnome-session-properties' and add the bash file on the 
list.
# 4) Enjoy !
